    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. you mentioned the revenue part... do people actually think it's a viable way to fund transit, or is that more of a talking point used to justify the tolls? like, is there a consensus on whether the environmental benefits actually outweigh the economic strain on commuters?",
